<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">

  <title>{{.Provider.PrettyName}} - About</title>

  <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro:400,700|Open+Sans:300italic,400,300,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="{{.StaticRoot}}favicon.ico">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/semantic-ui/0.16.1/css/semantic.min.css">

  <script type="text/javascript" src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/semantic-ui/0.16.1/javascript/semantic.min.js"></script>

  <style>

    html, body {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Open Sans", "Helvetica Neue", "Helvetica", "Arial", sans-serif;
      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
      color: #333333;
      background-color: #FCFCFC;
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="ui one column page grid">
<div class="one column row">
  <div class="column">
    <h2 class="ui dividing header">
      {{.Provider.PrettyName}}
    </h2>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="ui one column page grid">
  <div class="column">
    <h3 class="ui top attached black inverted header">{{.Provider.PrettyName}} Is...</h3>
    <div class="ui attached segment">

      {{range $line := .Provider.Description}}
      <p>{{$line}}</p>
      {{end}}

    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="column">
    <h3 class="ui top attached black inverted header">How to Play</h3>
    <div class="ui attached segment">
      <p>
        Different people play {{.Provider.PrettyName}} in different ways.
        Here's how we like to play it at my parties.
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>Gather everyone around the computer screen (fullscreen it!).</li>
        <li>Pick some filters everyone can agree on.</li>
        <li>Go around in a circle, everyone getting a turn.</li>
        <ol>
          <li>Look at a screenshot.</li>
          <li>If you can name exactly what it is, everyone else takes a drink and you go again.</li>
          <li>If you fail, you take a drink.</li>
          <li>If you got really close and everyone feels like taking pity on you, you get another try.</li>
        </ol>
        <li>(Optional) Let people 'steal' (guess out of turn) and take a drink (or 2!) if they fail. If they succeed, everyone else drinks and the turn order skips to them.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="column">
    <p>
      <div class="ui large inverted green confirm button" onclick="window.location='main'">
        Let's Play!
      </div>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
